#: chaotic_pfc.comms.channel.ideal_channel:3 of
msgid ""
"This is literally a copy of the input. It is still defined as a function "
"(rather than aliased to ``numpy.ndarray.copy``) so that the receiver-side"
" code can always call ``ideal_channel(s)`` consistently regardless of the"
" channel configuration chosen by the caller."
msgstr ""

